  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\nFor sharding, we switch all `HexaryTrie` to `BinaryTrie`.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\nMost changes are in `evm.db.chain.BaseChainDB`. I suggest we divide it into two parts:\r\n1. `master` branch:\r\n    * Make `trie_class` to be configurable in `BaseChainDB.__init__`.\r\n    * Default: `HexaryTrie`\r\n\r\n2. Rebase `sharding` branch and switch sharding-related tries to `BinaryTrie`.\r\n",
